                 Packages                          Resolve Dependencies
   --\ Keep the following packages at their current version:
 R   gstreamer0.8-cdparanoia                           [0.8.11-1 (unstable, now)]
 A   sound-juicer                                      [2.10.1-3 (unstable, now)]
















